                        <p style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>5-30 min: Deep work</strong> - Focused learning (Pomodoro 25
                            min block)</p>
                        <p style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>30-35 min: Break</strong> - Walk, water, fresh air</p>
                        <p style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>35-60 min: Practice</strong> - Problems, flashcards, practice
                            tests</p>
                        <p style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>60-65 min: Review</strong> - Summarize key points, plan next
                            session</p>
                    </div>
