                    <h4>The 80/20 Rule (Pareto Principle)</h4>
                    <p>80% of your results come from 20% of your effort. Identify the high-impact activities:</p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>üìå Core concepts (not side details)</li>
                        <li>üìå Practice problems (not just reading)</li>
                        <li>üìå Past exams (signal highest-priority content)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">Time Blocking Template</h4>
